all the responses I want.

100
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:16,760
Life on Balance Island is perfect.

101
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:27,230
Welcome to
the Balance Island Water Arena.

102
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,830
