287
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:19,550
Put it behind your back.

288
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,880
You can use both hands.

289
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,350
Defend well and hold your ground.

290
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:34,470
Sorry.

291
00:11:35,230 --> 00:11:36,840
