304
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,400
I'll pull you up from above.

305
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,670
Just make sure I look good.

306
00:12:36,670 --> 00:12:37,520
Thanks.

307
00:12:59,030 --> 00:13:00,840
I'm never teaming up with you again.

308
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:02,640
Come on, but look.

309
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:04,590
You grabbed the first ribbon,
didn't you?

310
00:13:05,030 --> 00:13:05,880
That was amazing.

311
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,030
You're incredible, babe.

312
00:13:08,860 --> 00:13:10,670
