318
00:13:32,470 --> 00:13:33,350
Soak yourself all the way.

319
00:13:33,640 --> 00:13:34,230
Or later...

320
00:13:34,230 --> 00:13:34,760
Get soaked.

321
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:36,640
Yeah, or you'll freeze later.

322
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:38,640
Yeah, you'll sink right in.

323
