333
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,790
Don't be scared, move forward.

334
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:22,350
Don't be afraid.

335
00:14:22,350 --> 00:14:22,790
Right.

336
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:23,790
Come on.

337
00:14:29,550 --> 00:14:30,230
Give it a go.

338
00:14:30,710 --> 00:14:31,640
No.

339
00:14:46,110 --> 00:14:46,960
Let's go!

340
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:56,780
