347
00:15:16,580 --> 00:15:19,660
(Guarding others' love;
Guarding my love)

348
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:23,710
Enda.

349
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:26,760
What?

350
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:31,790
Cool.

351
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:51,400
You're sticking like glue.

352
00:15:53,460 --> 00:15:55,740
