358
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:17,470
Your left wrist has no ribbon,
so don't worry.

359
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,910
Come on.

360
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:29,030
Attack with your left hand.

361
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:47,540
