with him again.

378
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:20,310
Yeah.

379
00:17:23,830 --> 00:17:25,040
Let's end this.

380
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,680
End it and let me go.

381
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:28,680
I wanna finish this,
but I wanna win more.

382
00:17:34,230 --> 00:17:34,830
