takes off the second ribbon and wins)

385
00:18:05,040 --> 00:18:05,880
Well done.

386
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:07,350
Impressive.

387
00:18:17,950 --> 00:18:20,110
When I saw Jiayi fighting so hard

388
00:18:20,110 --> 00:18:22,040
